---
title: Cheesy Bacon & Egg Butter Bun with Tomato & Caramelised Onion Relish | Serves 2
description: Everyone loves a good bacon and egg roll but we think this one is better than any of your cafe favourites. Stack up a butter bun
with oozy cheese, thyme, tomato and onion relish, crispy bacon. Top with an fried egg for the ultimate brunch bun!
